        "created_at": "2018-06-19T19:05:00.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"LMD Ermita\u00f1o\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n LMD Ermita\u00f1o:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Alan Rath\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Alan Rath:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Raveneau\u2019s Monts Mains is, pretty much every year, one of the more \u201crestrained\u201d wines in the portfolio - frankly, one of my favorites, because it says \u201cChablis\u201d more than the others to me.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>We really must have a meal (and some wine, of course) next I am in California. I believe we will have a nice time.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Would love to! I wasn\u2019t able to join the last dinner you had here a few years ago, hopefully some day it will happen  <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/0/0ff9bfcdb0964982cd3240b6159868fbdf215b1a.gif\" width=\"24\" height=\"18\" alt=\"[cheers.gif]\" title=\"cheers\" class=\"animated\"></p>",
